title: Polymaker brings polycarbonate materials to the 3D printing market
text: Polymaker brings polycarbonate materials to the 3D printing market 5 October 2015 Aaron Jennings from Polymaker tells TCT about the 3D printing material company's partnership with Covestro and why printing with polycarbonate-based materials will provide engineers and professional users with the ability to create and prototype real parts.
